<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.7">
<l>kōtaivē laivarkkāy maṇṇakalaṅ kūṟiṭuvāṉ</l>
<l>tūtaṉāy maṉṉavaṉāl colluṇṭāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>tūtaṉāy maṉṉavaṉāl colluṇṭā ṉākilum</l>
<l>ōtanīr vaiyakammu ṉuṇṭumiḻntāṉ cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! To give [just] a piece of the vast earth to the Five</l>
<l rend="indent">who had arm guards [and] spears,</l>
<l>As a messenger, he was commanded by a king.</l>
<l>Although as a messenger, he was commanded by a king,</l>
<l>He once ate and expelled the earth with flooding seas. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
